    {
        "content": "<p>github-actions[bot] <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13354#issuecomment-4444890416\">commented</a> on <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13354\">PR #13354</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<h4>Subscribe to Label Action</h4>\n<p>cc @cfallin, @fitzgen</p>\n<p>&lt;details&gt;<br>\nThis issue or pull request has been labeled: \"cranelift\", \"cranelift:area:aarch64\", \"cranelift:meta\", \"isle\"</p>\n<p>Thus the following users have been cc'd because of the following labels:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>cfallin: isle</li>\n<li>fitzgen: isle</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To subscribe or unsubscribe from this label, edit the &lt;code&gt;.github/subscribe-to-label.json&lt;/code&gt; configuration file.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/subscribe-to-label-action\">Learn more.</a><br>\n&lt;/details&gt;</p>\n</blockquote>",
